  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Each morning you can enjoy a continental breakfast, which will set you up for a busy day on the slopes. In the evenings, dinner is a three course meal with a fresh salad bar. For your 'primo piatto' (starter) you'll choose between warming pasta or soup which is followed by a main and a dessert. The style of food is traditional and comforting and the chefs love to put their own spin on classic Piemonte recipes. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
