  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Villa Cary is a small, family-run hotel with a warm and friendly atmosphere geared towards couples. Located in the centre of Sauze, you have great access to the resort amenities and the <a data-udi="umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c}" title="Milky Way Ski Area">Milky Way Ski Area</a>.</p>
<h2>Prime location</h2>
<p>It's located on <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/italy/milky-way-ski-area/sauze-doulx">Sauze d'Oulx's</a> main square just five minutes from the Clotes chairlift - a prime position for hitting the slopes. From the top of Clotes, you have access to a range of red runs, and can easily make your way up to the nearby resorts of Sestriere and Claviere before exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">French</a> side of the ski area over in Montgenevre.</p>
<h2>Alpine style</h2>
<p>The comfortable lounge area is a great place to relax after a day on the mountain. Enjoy a drink from the alpine-style bar before heading to the hotel's restaurant for a tasty three-course meal.</p>
<h2>Homely hotel</h2>
<p>Each of the homely bedrooms has a traditional feel, providing a comfortable retreat to relax after exploring one of the most extensive skiing areas in Europe. Many of the rooms also have a balcony, ideal for enjoying the winter sun. This is the perfect little base for couples who are looking for affordable accommodation close to to all the local amenities. This season the hotel has brand new beds and mattresses.</p>
<p>Groups of four or more people of the same sex are not accepted.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Villa Cary the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
